article.description: — Kane Williams registered 18 points as Georgia State got past Charlotte 76-65 on Friday night.
article.headline: Williams leads Georgia State over Charlotte 76-65
article.linkText: Williams leads Georgia State over Charlotte 76-65
article.story: CHARLOTTE, N.C. -- — Kane Williams registered 18 points as Georgia State got past Charlotte 76-65 on Friday night. JoJo Toppin had 16 points for Georgia State (3-1). Corey Allen added 14 points and Ryan Boyce had 10 points. Jahmir Young had 20 points for the 49ers (0-2). Jordan Shepherd added 15 points and Brice Williams had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
